TextEng: I should be going now.
Me go now.
Where can I find Haedraline?
Where me find Haedraline?
Lord Nasher, may I ask you some questions?
Text: 나셰르 영주님, 질문 몇 가지 해도 될까요?

TextEng: Me want ask you some stuff.
What can you tell me about Haedraline?
Text: 하에드랄린에 대해 뭘 말씀해 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: What can you tell me about the Words of Power that were brought here earlier?
Text: 앞서 여기로 가져온 권능의 언령에 대해 뭘 말씀해 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: What can you tell me about the Source Stone?
Text: 근원석에 대해 뭘 말씀해 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: What's the latest news from the battle lines?
I'm interested in knowing more about you, Lord Nasher.
Text: 나셰르 영주님에 대해 더 알고 싶습니다.

TextEng: What you know 'bout Haedraline lizard girly?
What you know 'bout Power Words that was brought here earlier?
Text: 전에 여기 가져온 권능의 언령 뭐 알아?

TextEng: What you know 'bout Source Stone?
You got news 'bout how war going?
Me want know stuff 'bout you.
Can you let Haedraline out of the dungeon?
Text: 하에드랄린을 감옥에서 내보내 주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Maybe you let lizard girly out of dungeon, 'kay?
I would like to ask you something else.
Me want ask you other stuff.
Where can I find Master Ford?
Text: 포드 박사는 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where me find Master Ford?
What if I could kill Aribeth and Maugrim?
Text: 제가 아리베스와 모그림을 죽일 수 있다면요?

TextEng: Is there no one who will come to our aid?
Text: 우리를 도우러 올 사람이 아무도 없나요?

TextEng: What if me kill Aribeth and Maugrim? That help, maybe.
Text: 내가 아리베스랑 모그림 죽이면 어때? 도움 될 것 같아.

TextEng: Ain't you got no friends who come help you?
I want to ask you about Aribeth.
Me want ask you 'bout Aribeth.
What do you mean?
What you mean?
You followed the law, Lord Nasher. You had no choice.
Text: 법을 따르신 겁니다, 나셰르 영주님. 선택의 여지가 없었어요.

TextEng: What is done is done, Lord Nasher. No sense dwelling on it now.
Text: 일어난 일은 일어난 겁니다, 나셰르 영주님. 지금 와서 거기 얽매일 필요 없어요.

TextEng: Fenthick's execution may have been wrong, but it does not excuse Aribeth's betrayal!
Text: 펜딕의 처형은 잘못되었을지 모르지만, 그렇다고 아리베스의 배신이 정당화되진 않습니다!

TextEng: You just follow the law. You not have choice.
It be done now. You waste time if you think of it when it all over.
Text: 이미 끝난 일이야. 다 끝났는데 계속 생각하는 건 시간 낭비야.

TextEng: It maybe wrong for you kill Fenthick, but that not make what Aribeth do right!
Text: 펜딕 죽인 건 잘못됐을 수도 있어. 근데 그래도 아리베스가 한 일은 옳지 않아!

TextEng: Perhaps you can atone for what you have done.
Maybe you got chance for make it all better.
Text: 지금이라도 더 좋게 만들 수 있을 거야.

TextEng: You're right. She deserves death.
Her death will only continue the cycle of vengeance and bloodshed.
Text: 그녀의 죽음은 복수와 유혈의 악순환을 이어갈 뿐입니다.

TextEng: You right. She need death.
You kill Aribeth, maybe someone else want come kill you. It never end.
Text: 아리베스 죽이면 다른 사람이 너 죽이러 올 거야. 끝이 없어.

TextEng: What are you planning to do with Aribeth?
What you gonna do with Aribeth?
Aribeth is in your dungeon? What are you talking about?
Aribeth be in you dungeon? What you talking about?
The law is the law, Lord Nasher. Aribeth deserves death.
Text: 법은 법입니다, 나셰르 영주님. 아리베스는 죽어 마땅합니다.

TextEng: There can be no forgiveness for what Aribeth has done, Lord Nasher. She deserves death.
Text: 아리베스가 한 일은 용서할 수 없습니다, 나셰르 영주님. 그녀는 죽어 마땅합니다.

TextEng: The law be the law. It say she need die, she get death.
Text: 법은 법이야. 법에서 죽으라고 하면 죽어야 돼.

TextEng: You not forgive her for what she done. Aribeth need death.
Text: 아리베스가 한 일 용서하면 안 돼. 죽어야 돼.
